snippet.title: Session: Skate Sim – Abandoned Mall DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
The skatepark skateboarders have been dreaming of. Check out the Abandoned Mall and find all the new spots where you can perform your best tricks. This DLC includes:
- The Abandoned Mall map
- 38 items for the object dropper

Session: Skate Sim is available on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, and on PC (Steam/Epic Games Store).
